OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,FResidents and businesses in the south
OL,7,Fof the Isle of Man have said they feel
OL,8,F'stranded', after the removal of a bus
OL,9,Fservice to the southernmost point of
OL,10,Fthe island.
OL,12,FBus Vannin's seasonal service to The
OL,13,FSound was scrapped in the summer of
OL,14,F2023, after the island's government
OL,15,Fdecided the route was not making
OL,16,Fenough money.
OL,18,FMargaret Holmes lives in The Howe, one
OL,19,Fof the villages on the route.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
