OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,FShe says the lack of public transport
OL,7,Fhas left some of the elderly residents
OL,8,Ffeeling 'stuck in their own home', as
OL,9,Fmany relied on the bus.
OL,11,FShe said: "There's no other way for
OL,12,Fpeople to either get to work at The
OL,13,FSound or Cregneash, visitor
OL,14,Fattractions, events that are on,
OL,15,Fyou've got to have a car to get there."
OL,17,FMargaret says some residents have been
OL,18,F'forced to provide the service'
OL,19,Fthemselves, after offering lifts to
OL,20,Ftourists making their own way down the
OL,21,Froute.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
