OL,6,FThe stretch of road starting at Port
OL,7,FErin runs to The Sound, often
OL,8,Fdescribed as one of the island's
OL,9,Fgreatest beauty spots.
OL,11,FEmily Thompson is manager of the Sound
OL,12,FCafe, and says the decision has left
OL,13,Fher struggling to recruit staff.
OL,15,FShe said: "We hire a lot of young
OL,16,Fpeople, a lot of whom can't drive. We
OL,17,Fhave full-time staff who're older who
OL,18,Fcan't drive, which is a huge issue.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
