OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,F"It's really taken a toll. We have
OL,7,Flots of customers still, but you do
OL,8,Fnotice a little less. There would be
OL,9,Frushes every hour when the bus came
OL,10,Fdown so there is a big difference
OL,11,Fsince we don't get it anymore."
OL,13,FThe Sound is popular with tourists,
OL,14,Foffering stunning views of the Calf of
OL,15,FMan, with regular sightings of seals
OL,16,Fin the wild.
OL,18,FEmily added: "You come over to the
OL,19,FIsle of Man - you're a tourist you
OL,20,Fwant to see this - you want to go to
OL,21,Fthe tourists hotspots.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
