OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,F"Tourists need public transport, so if
OL,7,Fyou can't get down here, then you're
OL,8,Fmissing out on possibly one of the
OL,9,Fbest things on the island I'd say."
OL,11,FAlso on the route is one of the
OL,12,Fisland's most treasured heritage sites
OL,13,F- a Manx village built to replicate
OL,14,Flife in the 1800s.
OL,16,FCregneash is the oldest open-air folk
OL,17,Fmuseum, and another key tourist
OL,18,Fattraction along the bus route.
