OL,6,FVolunteers working in the village say
OL,7,Fthey have seen a decrease in the
OL,8,Fnumber of visitors to the site, which
OL,9,Fthey say goes against the government's
OL,10,Fstrategy to increase tourism.
OL,12,FHead gardener, Brian Kewley said: "The
OL,13,Ffinancial side of things to put that
OL,14,Fbus on is minimal compared to what you
OL,15,Fget out of it.
