OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,F"The heritage of the island is
OL,7,Fexceptionally important and this is
OL,8,Fone of the most amazing places on the
OL,9,Fisland. If you're not fit you can't
OL,10,Fget here, so we need to get people to
OL,11,Fcome here - how do we do that? We need
OL,12,Fa bus."
OL,14,FStaff at the Rushen Heritage Centre in
OL,15,FPort Erin say they 'regularly deal
OL,16,Fwith angry visitors' trying to reach
OL,17,FThe Sound.
