OL,3,CResidents feel 'stranded' as future of
OL,4,Csouthern bus route remains uncertain
OL,6,FKathryn Potter from the Centre said:
OL,7,F"We can understand how they feel
OL,8,Fbecause it spoils their holiday if
OL,9,Fthey arrive in Port Erin expecting to
OL,10,Fgo to Cregneash and The Sound and find
OL,11,Fthat there isn't any public transport.
OL,13,F"We had a full summer of it last year,
OL,14,Fand we're bracing ourselves for a full
OL,15,Fsummer of it this year".
OL,17,FThe Isle of Man Government says while
OL,18,Fthey are reviewing the future of the
OL,19,Fbus route, it's future remains
OL,20,Funcertain.
