OL,6,FFounder of the campaign group 'Save
OL,7,Four Cregneash Bus', Christa Viohl said
OL,8,Fthat a decision needs to be made
OL,9,Fsooner rather than later, concluding
OL,10,Fthat the bus 'shouldn't be looked upon
OL,11,Fonly for profit'.
